## SEO Overhaul (March 12, 2026)

**Plan file**: `.cursor/plans/calacabana_seo_overhaul_4baa10ec.plan.md` — full audit + implementation plan

### All 6 Phases Implemented & Committed

**Phase 1 — Headings:**
- Header logo changed from `h1` to `span` (both Desktop + Mobile headers)
- DesktopHeader tagline `h3` -> `p`
- Homepage H1: "Alojamiento y alquileres vacacionales" (MonteCarlo cursive on mobile, regular font on desktop with " en Tanti, Cordoba" inline). "Tanti, Cordoba" as separate block on mobile (`fontSize="lg"`).
- Homepage H2: "Naturaleza, confort. Mirador de las sierras, en las sierras." (bold, MonteCarlo cursive on desktop `size="lg"`, default font on mobile `size="sm"`)
- Mobile-only tagline ("un mirador de las sierras, en las sierras") between Reviews and Map, `fontSize="4xl"` `fontWeight="semibold"`
- El-alojamiento: Single H1 "Sobre el alojamiento", three sections demoted to H2
- Ubicacion: H1 "Ubicacion en Tanti, Cordoba"
- 404: Added `as="h1"`

**Phase 2 — JSON-LD:**
- Created `components/seo/JsonLd.tsx` — reusable component + schema builders
- Global `LodgingBusiness` schema in `_app.tsx` (every page)
- Per-apartment schema on `/alojamiento/[apartment]` via `buildAccommodationSchema()`
- `Place` schema with geo coords on `/ubicacion` via `ubicacionPlaceSchema`
- Exact coordinates: -31.359358, -64.557336
- Full address: Calle Juarez Celman, Villa Serrana Keoken Manzana I Lote 13

**Phase 3 — Meta Tags:**
- Canonical `<link rel="canonical">` on every page
- `og:url` added to homepage, el-alojamiento, ubicacion (apartment pages already had it)
- Twitter Card tags (`twitter:card`, `twitter:title`, `twitter:description`, `twitter:image`) on every page
- Fixed `og:site_name` "Cala cabana" -> "Cala Cabana" in `_document.tsx`
- Fixed `ubicacion.tsx` og:image `.jpg` -> `.jpeg`

**Phase 4 — Meta Descriptions:**
- Homepage, apartment pages (dynamic template), el-alojamiento, ubicacion, 404 — all with unique Spanish descriptions
- `_document.tsx` fallback description updated

**Phase 5 — Semantic HTML:**
- `<section>` with aria-labels on homepage (apartments, reviews, map)
- `<article>` on apartment detail, `role="article"` on ApartmentCard, `<aside>` on booking sidebar
- `<a onClick>` -> `<Box as="button">` on carousel wrappers

**Phase 6 — Quick Wins:**
- Removed `user-scalable=0` from viewport meta
- Fixed typos: vegetación, combinación, Todo, reservado, nuestro
- Sitemap: lastmod, changefreq, priority, www prefix
- robots.txt: `Allow: /`, www prefix
- 404: Head with title, description, noindex, improved alt text

